summary: ...NARDA HOLDING STEADY WHILE CONTINUING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD... As of 8:00 PM PDT Fri Sep 26 the center of Narda was located near 17.3, -123.6 with movement WNW at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 979 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 90 mph.
